{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 <strong><u>About this game</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Welcome to a unique world!&quot;Otherwise&quot; is an exciting survival game filled with secrets and dangers.Here you can explore mysterious locations and encounter many monsters living in this universe.Do your best and get out of the depths of darkness!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 <strong><u>Explore</u></strong>\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Get resources to create powerful weapons and protective armor that will help you in battles with enemies!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316410/extras/\u0414\u043e\u0431\u044b\u0447\u0430_\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0443\u0440\u0441\u043e\u0432.png?t=1734902685\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316410/extras/\u041a\u0440\u0430\u0444\u0442.png?t=1734902685\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<strong><u>Diverse biomes</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore different biomes such as forests, deserts, mountainous areas and dungeons. Each biome offers unique resources, monsters, and climatic conditions, which requires players to adapt.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316410/extras/\u041b\u0435\u0441.png?t=1734902685\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"ht